Tony Ibarguen
Chief Executive Officer
Tony has served as Quench's CEO since he joined the company in 2010. He is also President of AquaVenture Holdings, Ltd., Quench's parent company, and serves on its Board of Directors. Tony has over 25 years of senior executive leadership experience at companies such as Insight Enterprises (NASDAQ: NSIT), a Fortune 500 information technology business where he also serves on its Board of Directors; Alliance Consulting Group, a privately-held IT consulting firm; and Tech Data (NASDAQ: TECD) a Fortune 500 global technology distributor. Tony holds a degree in Marketing from Boston College and an MBA from Harvard Business School.









